<p>The <code>decrement</code> tag subtracts 1 from a variable.</p>

<h2>Basic Decrement</h2>
<pre>{open}set $counter = 5{close}
Counter: {open}$counter{close}
{open}decrement $counter{close}
Counter: {open}$counter{close}
{open}decrement $counter{close}
Counter: {open}$counter{close}</pre>
{set $counter = 5}
<ul>
  <li>Counter: {$counter}</li>
  {decrement $counter}
  <li>Counter: {$counter}</li>
  {decrement $counter}
  <li>Counter: {$counter}</li>
</ul>

<h2>Countdown</h2>
<pre>{open}set $n = 5{close}
{open}while $n gt 0{close}
  {open}$n{close}...
  {open}decrement $n{close}
{open}/while{close}
Go!</pre>
{set $n = 5}
<p>
{while $n gt 0}
{$n}...
{decrement $n}
{/while}
Go!</p>

<h2>Decrement to Negative</h2>
{set $x = 2}
<pre>{open}set $x = 2{close}</pre>
<ul>
  <li>x = {$x}</li>
  {decrement $x}
  <li>x = {$x}</li>
  {decrement $x}
  <li>x = {$x}</li>
  {decrement $x}
  <li>x = {$x}</li>
</ul>
